snippet.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! Card EU | Yu-Gi-Oh! CROSS DUEL trailer
snippet.description:
Delivering a dynamic, fresh style of card battling, Yu-Gi-Oh! CROSS DUEL is a brand-new Yu-Gi-Oh! experience for up to four players. Featuring single-player, four-player versus and four-player co-op modes, Yu-Gi-Oh! CROSS DUEL offers something for everyone, whether they’re a Yu-Gi-Oh! veteran or a newcomer.

To mark the opening of pre-registration, KONAMI is offering special in-game rewards based on the number of people who pre-register for Yu-Gi-Oh! CROSS DUEL.

You can view how to pre-register for the game on the official CROSS DUEL website: https://www.konami.com/yugioh/crossduel



Be sure to Subscribe to our Channel and hit the alert bell to know when a new video is available! 
 
Stay up to date on Yu-Gi-Oh! TCG and Yu-Gi-Oh! Digital titles at http://www.yugioh-card.com
 
Facebook: https://facebook.com/YuGiOhCardEU
Twitch: https://twitch.tv/YuGiOhCardEU
Twitter: https://twitter.com/YuGiOhCardEU
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/YuGiOhCardEU
